{"tid":1067975,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧忍光：發佈境外辱國歌片犯法","createTime":"2019-03-19T02:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T10:10:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ce611e0a9f0d86624cfc5b94671d63ccf07204de","tid":1067975,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:15:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190319/20636560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190319%2F20636560&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKoV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=4e65b37f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190319%2F20636560&h=9f918b9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190319/20636560</a><br />\n<br />\n鄧忍光：發佈境外辱國歌片犯法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190319/large/0318wing3006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190319%2Flarge%2F0318wing3006.jpg&h=5df8a88e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政制及內地事務局常秘鄧忍光發佈境外辱國歌片犯法<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會《國歌條例草案》委員會昨日繼續審議，有議員關注若在境外侮辱國歌會否犯法，政制及內地事務局常秘鄧忍光稱，雖然有關法例不會規管境外行為，但若有人將有關片段拿回香港發放，一樣被視為犯法。鄧又拒回應草擬《國歌條例草案》時有否與中央交換意見。<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局長聶德權及其副局長昨未有出席《國歌條例草案》委員會，改由該局常秘鄧忍光回應議員提問。人民力量陳志全問鄧，若議員宣誓時不開口唱國歌是否有法律責任，鄧未能正面回應，只稱議員參選時已作公開聲明擁護《基本法》和效忠香港特區，「睇唔到會為議員造成任何不便」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：許智峯受傷 警入立會搜證<br />\n<br />\n拒交代與京溝通內容<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民鄭松泰問鄧，如港人在中國隊於卡塔爾比賽時侮辱國歌，有關片段上載互聯網或在電視中播出，是否觸犯《國歌法》？鄧指若該人士不是自己發佈有關影像，該行為又在境外發生，在普通法下不可能視為觸犯國歌法，但他稱若有人將有關片段拿回港發放，並在發放時有侮辱意圖就會觸犯國歌法。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨議員郭家麒則追問港府何時收中央政府指示要香港就國歌法立法，鄧拒作回應，遭郭炮轟在未諮詢巿民前，港府已「米已成炊」式宣佈立法。民主派議員毛孟靜亦多番要求鄧交代港府就《國歌法》立法與中央溝通內容，鄧同樣堅拒回應，毛批評：「呢個咪係專權、專橫嘅管治姿態囉！」<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n許智峯受傷 警入立會搜證<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n商防賄例受阻 郭榮鏗斥離譜<br />\n<br />\n許智峯受傷 警入立會搜證<br />\n趕立國歌法 廖長江限制議員提問"},{"pid":"9220bbc5ddf0b62c25bf0825d06879b053f04285","tid":1067975,"uid":183758,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:21:17.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦死支那<em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em>"},{"pid":"ed1f5f913bad25e52c0f3203327c2a9577225df1","tid":1067975,"uid":66618,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:22:53.000Z","msg":"ugly chink"},{"pid":"d82680bc83fbc461677fbb2301eed3c9cbcba840","tid":1067975,"uid":142888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:26:01.000Z","msg":"支那豚"},{"pid":"d753250b3cafd1c518af4986835fd48c7d0186de","tid":1067975,"uid":94054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/video/china/1602745/venezuela-military-band-plays-out-tune-chinese-anthem-welcome-ceremony\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fvideo%2Fchina%2F1602745%2Fvenezuela-military-band-plays-out-tune-chinese-anthem-welcome-ceremony&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKoV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=accd433e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/video/china/1602745/venezuela-military-band-plays-out-tune-chinese-anthem-welcome-ceremony</a><br />\n呢班人點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好拉我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d02d60715699307b5646fada619b84337ccf669","tid":1067975,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"ching chong"},{"pid":"fb71ae372484356ea199d30e6e6395dd97240268","tid":1067975,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:12:29.000Z","msg":"侮辱(中共國)國旗圖/片呢？"},{"pid":"135a10e52b03ace72bdc1d514aebedca8ab8ab78","tid":1067975,"uid":156511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:15:55.000Z","msg":"期待睇政府